  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find any glitches, be sure to email us at <a href=\"mailto:\"thebughouseofficial@gmail.com\"\">\"thebughouseofficial@gmail.com\"</a> with the subject line \"Freeky Faucets Arcade Glitch\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Freeky Faucets, you play as these round beetle bugs called <strong>Boogas.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/e9ffda706fc5cf541bcdbccab8a088f4.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PRESSING MATTERS! The <strong>Faucets</strong> have invaded ally grounds! Eeeyikes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.poster.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.webm?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.mp4?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry hero, <strong>Faucet Friend</strong> will assist! (for a price). Discover his comrades too! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/91ffdababedbdea1af8f3ca34407974e.poster.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/91ffdababedbdea1af8f3ca34407974e.webm?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/91ffdababedbdea1af8f3ca34407974e.mp4?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using your unique abilities, you can take down the Faucets, and recover your lost territory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/ae3d24960fed6d6c8c6a052ad16d0f51.poster.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/ae3d24960fed6d6c8c6a052ad16d0f51.webm?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/ae3d24960fed6d6c8c6a052ad16d0f51.mp4?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Here's some of the fantastic faucet features!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 unique characters</strong> with legs and weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power-ups</strong> and <strong>special abilities.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ base items</strong> to acquire.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>19 unlocks.</strong> Find my secrets!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under 8 locales! <strong>(3 sectors).</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dangerous weather.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scaling difficulty.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Paradice can teach you in <strong>Helper Mode!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the ultimate challenge in <strong>Grandpa Mode...</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acapella soundscape</strong> with awe-inspiring <strong>voice acting.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack by <strong>Stashclub!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AND <strong>MORE !!!</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>[CURRENT OBJECTIVE] CONTAIN SPECIMEN - PREVENT SPREAD</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find any glitches, be sure to email us at <a href=\"mailto:\"thebughouseofficial@gmail.com\"\">\"thebughouseofficial@gmail.com\"</a> with the subject line \"Freeky Faucets Arcade Glitch\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Freeky Faucets, you play as these round beetle bugs called <strong>Boogas.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/e9ffda706fc5cf541bcdbccab8a088f4.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PRESSING MATTERS! The <strong>Faucets</strong> have invaded ally grounds! Eeeyikes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.poster.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.webm?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/f0ebd2f815e77bf5cff637d830ca499e.mp4?t=1737007795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry hero, <strong>Faucet Friend</strong> will assist! (for a price). Discover his comrades too! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/91ffdababedbdea1af8f3ca34407974e.poster.avif?t=1737007795\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348710/extras/91ff